  "keyPointsSummary": [
    "'Let' means giving permission or allowing someone to do something",
    "Formula: Let + person + base verb (no 'to')",
    "Negative: Do not let / Don't let",
    "'Let me' = mujhe karne do; 'Let him/her' = use karne do"
